Blurb:: Number of collocation points to estimate PCE coefficients

Description::
Specify the number of collocation points used to estimate PCE
coefficients using regression or orthogonal-least-interpolation.

<b> Usage Tips </b>

For most use cases, this keyword will specify a single integer number
of points.  In more advanced UQ studies with hierarchical models, the
list of integers can apply to different models and/or model levels

